reviewText: My special needs granddaughter loves these Dora DVDs. They play over and over, without having to restart them! She is 12 years old, and has microcephaly.  She loves the music in these, I suspect.  She does not like the Mermaid DVD in a different set. She is non-verbal, so I will never know what is special about these Dora stories. But this 3 pack are her favorites!
My daughter loves Dora and this was a cute one! She likes this dvd and watches it a lot
Nice price and easy to buy!

Received wrong movie in box set, movie advertised was replaced with a differant movie,very disappointed with this as well as the child was upset. Hope they do the right thing and send the right movie s I do a lot of buying from them. I will begin to look elsewhere for my purchases if they don't make this right. It feels like a bait and switch!
Was bought for granddaughter's birthday....she loves Dora and fell in love with this.  She gets hours of enjoyment from this.
my daughter really likes dora to get this at a cheap price is a deal she will get her use out of it thanks alot
I bought these for my daughter for Christmas and she will not put them down. Gonna have to get more for when she wears them out!
All I can say is that my son loves dora and it goes the same for these DVD's. He has watched them 100 times and they are now part of his dvd collection......
